{
  "stem": "9262.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then, once it was finished, that was the end of the story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody was at work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we changed work, alternative work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went from one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to register, of course, in our workplace.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they always asked, why did you leave this?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to give a reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Either we wanted to work with our friends who were also working in the same factory, or we were living in a different vicinity, or we would say we had some domestic problems.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We always had to give a reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they took us on because-- if they needed workers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were only too glad if somebody wanted to come and work in their factory, rather than being in the factory where one was before.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was no problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So after a while, I went to that children colony.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because Rumkowski, the chairman-- he was a benefactor to children, especially to orphans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He loved orphans because he never had children of his own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he tried to protect the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he gave them more than the adults.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on that colony, I was well looked after.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now before I came on this colony, I had to go through a medical examination.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was in the winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have much to wear at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the young woman who was the director of the children's colony saw me shivering.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She says, oh, better take him inside and give him some clothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was given underwear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was given a suit, socks and shoes, and an overcoat, and a hat, which was superb, by that standard.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this was only given to the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
